Story: Acre or "Akko" one of the oldest cities in the Middle East today Israel. Its under siege
by Terrorist group. Local militia gear up to fight the  terrorist or the population will be
killed by the explosions.

Info: This map is not that good since is my first css ever map so i was, experimenting.
map is not good optimized, (only with func_detail and func_occluder) cause i couldn't learn hint and skip, and i don't care really since this will be my last css map. SO Warning FPS may fall to 80 in some areas. Have Fun.
